    "name": "Steady, Steady, Steady!",
    "steam_appid": 3217780,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/474626c350c4830955e7e158acd2a622.poster.avif?t=1771495035\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/474626c350c4830955e7e158acd2a622.webm?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/474626c350c4830955e7e158acd2a622.mp4?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/e2295bebd369951647a5f15e6c670cbb.avif?t=1771495035\" width=616 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join the team -</strong> Could you deliver a giant cake or a priceless vase? How about a snowman or a fallen star? You've got the job!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join a tiny team of robots and work together to make your deliveries. Balance your cargo through all kinds of wild weather, chaotic challenges and puzzling obstacles. Can you reach the goal with your delivery still intact? Can you land the perfect delivery? 📦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the team and play in 1 or 2 players in couch co-op. 🕹️🕹️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/bf603d02f412722617eeb2b409abb7d5.avif?t=1771495035\" width=616 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plays solo or local Co-op. 🕹️🕹️</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with a buddy and grab another controller or share a keyboard. Work together to find the perfect balance to navigate your delivery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try your hand at controlling both characters when playing solo, or bring a friend along for a co-op game and each take control of one of the team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/5790e30f056157eb9d70e2dc3b416c8f.avif?t=1771495035\" width=616 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make new friends - </strong>Meet a whole host of colourful characters who have unique jobs and challenges waiting for you. Collect team photos with all your happy customers after completing their tasks and earn bonuses for the perfect delivery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/51b8777b5a666600e7b1a8498c1f8618.webp?t=1771495035\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/cbe1da8daeb13f941b776c3774e97739.poster.avif?t=1771495035\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/cbe1da8daeb13f941b776c3774e97739.webm?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/cbe1da8daeb13f941b776c3774e97739.mp4?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Which one will you find? 🎊</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and collect all kinds of tiny clockwork toy robots. Take a break from your deliveries to build a robot and watch them roll, fly and walk around the break room. 🎁🎊🤖 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/1713127e7dddb76b7b5c2bde2877b467.avif?t=1771495035\" width=616 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready for little break from your deliveries? How about going head to head with a friend in some mini games or take on some chaotic challenges.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See how high can you fly and take on the Golden Cog challenge. Navigate through an endless level that generates all kinds of chaotic obstacles. ⚙️</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How about a day at the beach with a game of volley ball and see who can score the most points while catching some rays. 🏖️☀️</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delivery dash 📦- Who will be the first to make their delivery? Each player goes head to head  to see who can make their delivery in the speediest time. ⏰</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/71085a3d0cb35deda2cf60bd9756b659.poster.avif?t=1771495035\" width=616 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/71085a3d0cb35deda2cf60bd9756b659.webm?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/71085a3d0cb35deda2cf60bd9756b659.mp4?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Cog Shop is now OPEN!</strong> 🎩⚙️- Pop on by the local Cog Shop, where you can spend your hard earned cogs on new hats, accessories and other shiny collectables. ✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/4401cc5975c53433eae74cb9898d7209.poster.avif?t=1771495035\" width=412 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/4401cc5975c53433eae74cb9898d7209.webm?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/4401cc5975c53433eae74cb9898d7209.mp4?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/564605f96befcb2c6f97e8cf6281f934.poster.avif?t=1771495035\" width=174 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/564605f96befcb2c6f97e8cf6281f934.webm?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/564605f96befcb2c6f97e8cf6281f934.mp4?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/6c458759c263ed87425263bf88fa47f9.poster.avif?t=1771495035\" width=588 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/6c458759c263ed87425263bf88fa47f9.webm?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217780/extras/6c458759c263ed87425263bf88fa47f9.mp4?t=1771495035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm having a really fun time working on <strong>Steady, Steady, Steady!</strong> If you would like to stay updated with the games progress and on any other projects, you can check out my website or follow along on my socials. I really appreciate all the feedback I receive on the game and I'm excited to be releasing the game on Steam soon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks a lot,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chris - Cloud Lantern.</p>",
